Marketing Workspace

---

## Founder Promise

The Marketing Workspace empowers founders with a clear, executive-level understanding of their marketing performance, enabling them to identify opportunities, address risks, and make confident marketing decisions within one minute.

---

## Success Criteria

A founder should be able to understand the overall marketing health of the business within 60 seconds, identify the highest-priority opportunities and risks, and know the next recommended action without opening another workspace.

